Constructor Detail

LinearSearch

public LinearSearch(SearchFilterIF filter)
Constructs a new LinearSearch object with the specified filter. The filter is used to determine whether objecs in the collection match the search criteria. The LinearSearch object traverses the collection linearly testing each object for membership, and then adding it to the overall set of results if the criteria holds.
Parameters:
filter:Ljjb.toolbox.util.SearchFilterIF - used to determine set membership of the objects in the collection matching the search criteria.
